<scriptment id="77000" point="dan_kyou" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-10-20" status="final">
	<part>
		<comment>Sporadic event. Occurs the day after Dan loses his home.</comment>
	    <condition>
	        <narration>Yuki did not lend Dan rent money.</narration>
	        <narration>Dan stands at a man's apartment door with box in hand. The future roommate's door opens, out of it comes Kyou.</narration>
	        <line id="1000" speaker="kyou" voicelang="ja">Yo.</line>
	        <line id="2000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">Sup.</line>
	        <condition>
	        	<comment>Player did not hire Kyou.</comment>
	  			<narration>Yuki flails.</narration>
	        	<line id="3000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Hello!</line>
	        	<narration>Kyou glares at Yuki. He looks back at Dan.</narration>
	        	<line id="4000" speaker="kyou" voicelang="ja">This person's stingy, huh?</line>
	        	<narration>The two laugh.</narration>
	        </condition>
	        <line id="5000" speaker="kyou" voicelang="ja">It would be so much easier if you lended Dan some cash.</line>
	        <line id="6000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I pay his wages, not his vices.</line>
	        <narration>Kyou sighs.</narration>
	        <line id="7000" speaker="kyou" voicelang="ja">Dan, I'll show you around.</line>
	        <line id="8000" speaker="kyou" voicelang="ja">Yuki, stay outside.</line>
	        <narration>Yuki sighs. The wind blows.</narration>
	    </condition>
	</part>
</scriptment>